message: Dear Bob, I am excited to present our premium product, which has been meticulously designed and crafted to exceed expectations. This exceptional item carries a significant value of $12000 to me, reflecting its quality, uniqueness, and the time invested in its creation. I am extending this opportunity to you with an offer of $15000. This price not only acknowledges the product's worth but also allows for a reasonable profit margin for me. I believe this offer presents a valuable opportunity for both of us. Please let me know if you would like to proceed with this offer.
